    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
      <div class="col-sm-10">
        <div class="what-we-do-subsection">
          <h4><i class="primary-color fas fa-hands-helping"></i> Guidance</h4>
          <p>Get assistance, no matter what stage you're at, from our carefully <br>
            vetted experts- all current students, alumni, or former <br>
            admissions counselors from top universities</p>
        </div>

        <div class="what-we-do-subsection">
          <h4><i class="primary-color fas fa-pen-fancy"></i> Application</h4>
          <p>Not feeling too confident with an essay or a personal statement? <br>
          Let our experts take a second look. Or a third. Or a fourth. Let's <br>
          get it right, together.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
      <div class="col-sm-10">
        <div class="what-we-do-subsection">
          <h4><i class="primary-color fas fa-search"></i> Discovery</h4>
          <p>Let us help you find the right higher education institution for you<br>
          not what a ranking list says</p>
        </div>

        <div class="what-we-do-subsection">
